      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW BALLISTA (1) was a little disappointing last start at Warragul when 4th (23.51) over 400m. Has never missed the frame here at the trip including one win. Won at his only start from this box. Tough to beat if on-song. WATCH IT (7) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Crackerjack Gus (22.94) in a Mix 6/7. The form from his last run stacks up well. Can measure up this time. ALL NET (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 23.06 beating NEBULA BALE. Has never been out of the placings from three starts out of this box. Can make it back-to-back wins. CUCUZZA (6) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
